<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181767>
    dc:description "FIGURE 10. Fresh specimens. Turleania saliens n. sp., holotype male (sl 3.3 mm), CMNH-ZC 0 2187 (A, B); Turleania saliens n. sp., paratype female (sl 2.9 mm), CMNH-ZC 0 2191 (C); Turleania tenebrosa n. sp., holotype male (sl 3.0 mm), CMNH-ZC 0 0 932 (D). A, D, entire specimen, dorsal view; B, same, anterior view; C, carapace and cephalic appendages, dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181767/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181760>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Turleania saliens n. sp. A – G, I, holotype male (sl 3.3 mm), CMNH-ZC 02187; H, paratype female (sl 2.9 mm), CMNH-ZC 0 2191. A, shield and cephalic appendages, dorsal view (setae omitted from left side); B, shield and posterior carapace, dorsal view (setae omitted from left side); C, sixth thoracic sternite, ventral view; D, coxae of fifth pereopods and eighth thoracic sternite, ventral view; E, basis and sexual tube of left fifth pereopod, lateral view; F, left sexual tube, distal part, dorsal view; G, H, telson, dorsal view; I, left fourth pereopod, dactylus, propodus, and distal part of carpus, lateral view. Scales equal 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181760/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181761>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Turleania saliens n. sp. Holotype male (sl 3.3 mm), CMNH-ZC 0 2187. A, left mandible, internal view; B, left maxillule, ventral view; C, left maxilla, ventral view; D, left first maxilliped, ventral view; E, left second maxilliped, ventral view; F, left third maxilliped, lateral view; G, same, proximal segments, mesial view (setae omitted). Scales equal 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181761/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181762>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Turleania saliens n. sp. Holotype male (sl 3.3 mm), CMNH-ZC 0 2187. A, right cheliped, mesial view; B, same, lateral view; C, same, chela, dorsal view (setae omitted from fingers); D, same, carpus, dorsal view; E, left cheliped, chela and carpus, dorsal view (setae omitted from fingers). Scales equal 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181762/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.181763>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Turleania saliens n. sp. Holotype male (sl 3.3 mm), CMNH-ZC 0 2187. A, left cheliped, mesial view; B, same, lateral view; C, right second pereopod, lateral view; D, same, dactylus and distal part of propodus, mesial view (setae omitted); E, left third pereopod, lateral view; F, same, dactylus and distal part of propodus, mesial view (setae omitted). Scales equal 1.0 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/181763/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

